name: Discreet Landmarks II - Presstube HQ
description: Presstube HQ is the second piece in the Discreet Landmarks series - 2018. Discreet landmarks are capable of modifying their properties in order to be able to differentiate themselves from their surrounding environment. Special thanks to Presstube for letting me capture his studio back then. High resolution/4K video available for collectors on request. Twitter: @smallfly
